Introduction

Yoon Eun Hye is a South Korean actress, singer, and model and director under Favor Entertainment. She debuted in 1999 as a sub vocalist for the now disbanded girl group BABY V.O.X, yet left in 2005 to embark on a solo career. She is the founder of Favor Entertainment.
